        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="个人博客搭建过程">个人博客搭建过程</h1><p>可以使用Halo、Hexo</p><h1 id="hexo">Hexo</h1><h2 id="下载git">下载git</h2><h2 id="安装hexo">安装Hexo</h2><p>管理员权限</p><h2 id="生成永久链接">生成永久链接</h2><p><code>hexo-abbrlink</code> 是一个 Hexo 插件，用于为每篇文章生成唯一且永久的链接，即使文章的日期或标题发生变化，链接也不会改变。</p><h3 id="安装和配置">安装和配置</h3><ol><li><p><strong>安装插件：</strong></p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-abbrlink --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>配置hexo根目录的 <code>_config.yml</code>：</strong></p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">permalink:</span> <span class="string">posts/:abbrlink/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># or</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">permalink:</span> <span class="string">posts/:abbrlink.html</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="示例链接结构">示例链接结构</h3><ul><li><strong>crc32 &amp; hex:</strong> <code>https://yourdomain.com/posts/8ddf18fb.html</code></li><li><strong>crc32 &amp; dec:</strong> <code>https://yourdomain.com/posts/1690090958.html</code></li></ul><p>更多详情请访问 <a href="https://github.com/ohroy/hexo-abbrlink">hexo-abbrlink GitHub 页面</a>。</p><h3 id="abbrlink-配置项详细说明"><code>abbrlink</code> 配置项详细说明</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># abbrlink config</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">abbrlink:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">alg:</span> <span class="string">crc32</span>      <span class="comment">#support crc16(default) and crc32</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">rep:</span> <span class="string">hex</span>        <span class="comment">#support dec(default) and hex</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">drafts:</span> <span class="literal">false</span>   <span class="comment">#(true)Process draft,(false)Do not process draft. false(default) </span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Generate categories from directory-tree</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># depth: the max_depth of directory-tree you want to generate, should &gt; 0</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">auto_category:</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span>  <span class="comment">#true(default)</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attr">depth:</span>        <span class="comment">#3(default)</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attr">over_write:</span> <span class="literal">false</span> </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">auto_title:</span> <span class="literal">false</span> <span class="comment">#enable auto title, it can auto fill the title by path</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">auto_date:</span> <span class="literal">false</span> <span class="comment">#enable auto date, it can auto fill the date by time today</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">force:</span> <span class="literal">false</span> <span class="comment">#enable force mode,in this mode, the plugin will ignore the cache, and calc the abbrlink for every post even it already had abbrlink. This only updates abbrlink rather than other front variables.</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">abbrlink:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">alg:</span> <span class="string">crc32</span>      <span class="comment"># 支持 crc16（默认）和 crc32。指定用于生成链接的算法。</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">rep:</span> <span class="string">hex</span>        <span class="comment"># 支持 dec（默认）和 hex。指定生成链接的表示形式。</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">drafts:</span> <span class="literal">false</span>   <span class="comment"># (true)处理草稿, (false)不处理草稿。默认值为 false。</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">auto_category:</span>  <span class="comment"># 从目录树生成分类</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span>  <span class="comment"># 启用自动分类，默认值为 true。</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attr">depth:</span> <span class="number">3</span>      <span class="comment"># 目录树的最大深度，必须大于 0。默认值为 3。</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attr">over_write:</span> <span class="literal">false</span>  <span class="comment"># 是否覆盖已有的分类，默认值为 false。</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">auto_title:</span> <span class="literal">false</span> <span class="comment"># 启用自动标题，可以根据路径自动填充标题。</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">auto_date:</span> <span class="literal">false</span>  <span class="comment"># 启用自动日期，可以根据今天的时间自动填充日期。</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">force:</span> <span class="literal">false</span>      <span class="comment"># 启用强制模式。在这种模式下，插件将忽略缓存，并为每篇文章重新计算 abbrlink，即使它已经有 abbrlink。此选项只会更新 abbrlink，而不会更新其他前端变量。</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="每一项的含义">每一项的含义</h3><ul><li><code>alg</code>: 用于生成链接的算法。<code>crc16</code> 和 <code>crc32</code> 都是不同的校验算法，<code>crc32</code> 会生成更长的链接。</li><li><code>rep</code>: 生成链接的表示形式。<code>dec</code> 表示十进制（如 <code>1690090958</code>），<code>hex</code> 表示十六进制（如 <code>8ddf18fb</code>）。</li><li><code>drafts</code>: 是否处理草稿。<code>true</code> 表示处理草稿，<code>false</code> 表示不处理草稿。</li><li><code>auto_category</code>: 自动分类相关配置。<ul><li><code>enable</code>: 是否启用自动分类。<code>true</code> 表示启用，<code>false</code> 表示禁用。</li><li><code>depth</code>: 自动分类的目录树最大深度，必须大于 0。</li><li><code>over_write</code>: 是否覆盖已有的分类。<code>true</code> 表示覆盖，<code>false</code> 表示不覆盖。</li></ul></li><li><code>auto_title</code>: 是否启用自动标题。<code>true</code> 表示启用，<code>false</code> 表示禁用。</li><li><code>auto_date</code>: 是否启用自动日期。<code>true</code> 表示启用，<code>false</code> 表示禁用。</li><li><code>force</code>: 是否启用强制模式。在强制模式下，插件将忽略缓存并为每篇文章重新计算 <code>abbrlink</code>，即使文章已经有 <code>abbrlink</code>。这仅会更新 <code>abbrlink</code>，不会更新其他前端变量。</li></ul><p>这些配置项可以帮助你更好地管理和生成 Hexo 博客中的永久链接，从而确保链接的稳定性和唯一性。</p><p>在 <code>abbrlink</code> 配置项中，<code>depth</code> 的作用是指定自动分类时目录树的最大深度。其具体含义如下：</p><h3 id="depth"><code>depth</code></h3><ul><li><strong>描述</strong>: 这个选项决定了自动生成分类目录时，目录树的最大层级深度。</li><li><strong>要求</strong>: 必须大于 0。</li><li><strong>默认值</strong>: 3。</li></ul><h3 id="示例解释">示例解释</h3><p>假设你有以下目录结构：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span></span><br><span class="line">└── _posts</span><br><span class="line">    ├── category1</span><br><span class="line">    │   ├── subcategory1</span><br><span class="line">    │   │   └── post1.md</span><br><span class="line">    │   └── subcategory2</span><br><span class="line">    │       └── post2.md</span><br><span class="line">    └── category2</span><br><span class="line">        └── post3.md</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果 <code>depth</code> 设置为 2，那么 <code>post1.md</code> 和 <code>post2.md</code> 会被归类到 <code>category1/subcategory1</code> 和 <code>category1/subcategory2</code>，但不会再进一步生成更深层次的分类。如果 <code>depth</code> 设置为 1，那么所有文章都会只归类到一级目录（如 <code>category1</code> 和 <code>category2</code>），而不会进一步细分到子目录。</p><p>通过配置 <code>depth</code>，你可以控制自动分类时目录结构的复杂程度，从而适应你的网站组织需求。</p><h2 id="inject">inject</h2><p>对于多行内容，通常需要使用块样式字符串。在这种情况下，你可以使用 | 或 &gt; 来表示多行文本。</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- |</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="language-javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-javascript">    <span class="comment">// 初始化 Sakana Widget</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-javascript">    <span class="title class_">SakanaWidget</span>.<span class="title function_">init</span>(&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-javascript">        <span class="attr">el</span>: <span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">getElementById</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;sakana-widget&#x27;</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-javascript">        <span class="comment">// 其他初始化选项</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-javascript">    &#125;);</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-javascript">  </span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://nickxu.me/2022/04/17/Hexo-Butterfly-%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%99%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AB%EF%BC%89%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-KaTeX-%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%8F/">https://nickxu.me/2022/04/17/Hexo-Butterfly-建站指南（八）使用-KaTeX-数学公式/</a></p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/zzq0523/article/details/122954271">设置网站投稿没有顶部图</a></p><p>待办事项</p><ul><li>[ ] 归档、分类、标签的top_img</li><li>[ ] 摄影动态、动态的实现</li><li>[ ] 网站图标、个人头像、404page约稿:smile:</li></ul><p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></msubsup><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mtext> </mtext><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\int_{a}^{b} f(x) \, dx = F(b) - F(a)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:2.5109580000000005em;vertical-align:-0.9119499999999999em;"></span><span class="mop"><span class="mop op-symbol large-op" style="margin-right:0.44445em;position:relative;top:-0.0011249999999999316em;">∫</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.5990080000000004em;"><span style="top:-1.7880500000000001em;margin-left:-0.44445em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">a</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.812900000000001em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">b</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.9119499999999999em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">x</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="mord mathdefault">x</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">b</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span><span clas